message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which I believe is worth more than $120 to you. To start our negotiation, I am offering it at $150. Please let me know if this is within your budget or if you'd like to propose a counteroffer.
I appreciate your offer, but I'm looking to save as much as possible. I'm willing to pay $120 for the product. Would you be willing to accept this price?
